OL,3,CFlixborough disaster 50th anniversary
OL,4,Cexhibition opens
OL,6,FAn exhibition to commemorate the 50th
OL,7,Fanniversary of the Flixborough
OL,8,Fdisaster has opened in .
OL,10,FShortly before 5pm on 1 June 1974, a
OL,11,Fmassive vapour cloud exploded at the
OL,12,FNypro chemical plant in Flixborough,
OL,13,Fnear , killing 28 people and leaving
OL,14,F36 seriously injured.
OL,16,FThe blast destroyed houses in the
OL,17,Fvillage, and was heard as far away as
OL,18,Fand .
OL,20,FAt the time, it was the largest
OL,21,Fpeacetime explosion in Britain.
