OL,6,FAs the 50th anniversary of the tragedy
OL,7,Fapproaches, has opened a new
OL,8,Fexhibition at the North Lincolnshire
OL,9,FMuseum in Scunthorpe, after inviting
OL,10,Fpeople to contribute their memories
OL,11,Fand items associated with the disaster.
OL,13,F"I ran downstairs, the door had been
OL,14,Fblown off, and I came out to see the
OL,15,Fmetal flying up into the air and a
OL,16,Fhuge black cloud billowing up in to
OL,17,Fthe sky," said one witness, Andrew
OL,18,FGreen.
OL,20,F"(It's) a very, very vivid memory."
