OL,6,F"When you look back at the news
OL,7,Ffootage, and the video footage, it's
OL,8,Fjust incredible the intensity and the
OL,9,Fscale of the fire afterwards."
OL,11,FEveline van Breemen is a collections
OL,12,Fassistant at the museum. She said the
OL,13,Fcollection of items and memories means
OL,14,Fvisitors can "really imagine" what the
OL,15,Fday would have been like for people
OL,16,Fwho were there.
