OL,6,F"One lady wrote in about how her
OL,7,Fbrother passed away that day - and it
OL,8,Ftook them four days to find him - but
OL,9,Fall the time they still had a little
OL,10,Fbit of hope even though they knew it
OL,11,Fwas very unlikely," she said.
OL,13,F"When you read that - yeah, definitely
OL,14,Fgoosebumps."
OL,16,FThe exhibition runs until November.
